Name: bs_assign_pass
Author: katsklaw
Category: BotServ
Last updated: 2008-10-04T17:17:46+01:00

Allows Admins to password protect /bs ASSIGN

in services.conf:

[b]BSAssignPass \"ubersecretpass\"[/b]

Optionally you can also require roots to use a password as well

[b]BSAssignPassRoot[/b]

Version 1.0.1 supports Anope 1.8.3
